- cs.SE (Software Engineering): The paper discusses the behavior of programs and how they can be controlled by an execution environment, which are topics related to software engineering.
- cs.FL (Formal Languages and Automata Theory): The paper discusses regular threads and their expressiveness, which are topics related to formal languages and automata theory.
